Lara said: ""It's great to have one world record, but now I'm so close to  another I'll be doing all I can to get it.
"Hopefully, the weather will hold to give me a chance. If it does I'll be  trying my hardest. This was the most satisfying of the hundreds in England  because it helped us win the game.
"I still can't quite believe what is happening to me. The interest since I  arrived in England has been tremendous and I'm just glad to be in good enough  form to meet expectations."
